properties.areaDesc: Port Washington to North Point Light WI; Sheboygan to Port Washington WI; Wind Point WI to Winthrop Harbor IL; North Point Light to Wind Point WI
properties.headline: Small Craft Advisory issued February 20 at 1:51PM CST until February 22 at 3:00AM CST by NWS Milwaukee/Sullivan WI
properties.description:
...GUSTY WINDS AND HIGH WAVES FRIDAY INTO FRIDAY NIGHT...

* WHAT...Southwest winds 15 to 25 kt with gusts up to 30 kt and
waves 2 to 4 feet expected.

* WHERE...Sheboygan WI to Winthrop Harbor IL.

* WHEN...From 9 AM Friday to 3 AM CST Saturday.

* IMPACTS...Conditions will be hazardous to small craft.
properties.instruction:
Inexperienced mariners, especially those operating smaller
vessels, should avoid navigating in hazardous conditions.

NWSheadline: SMALL CRAFT ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM 9 AM FRIDAY TO 3 AM CST SATURDAY
